Package de.espirit.firstspirit.store.access.nexport

Interface FsMetaExportInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExportInfo
    public interface FsMetaExportInfo
extends ExportInfo
    This interface represents the FirstSpirit only related meta information stored in directory .FirstSpirit. This type is always marked as updated. When using a VCS, the fs-meta files should be ignored (do not checkin).
    Since:
    5.2.1403
    See Also:
    ExportInfo, ExportOperation.Result, Schema
